#. type: Title #
#: ../src/guide/structure/package.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Using packages"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/structure/package.md
msgid ""
"Reusable code is distributed as [Composer packages](https://getcomposer.org/"
"doc/05-repositories.md#package).  A package can be an infrastructure "
"library, a Yii integration, a reusable feature, or a module representing an "
"application context."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/structure/package.md
msgid ""
"This page explains how to use packages in an application. To create a Yii-"
"aware package, see [Designing packages for Yii applications](designing-"
"packages.md)."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ##
#: ../src/guide/structure/package.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Installing packages <span id=\"installing-packages\"></span>"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/structure/package.md
msgid ""
"By default, Composer installs packages registered on [Packagist](https://"
"packagist.org/), the main repository for open source PHP packages."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/structure/package.md
msgid "Install a package with:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Fenced code block (sh)
#: ../src/guide/structure/package.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "composer require vendor-name/package-name\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/structure/package.md
msgid "Composer updates two files:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: ../src/guide/structure/package.md
msgid "`composer.json` stores the package name and version constraint."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: ../src/guide/structure/package.md
msgid "`composer.lock` stores the exact versions installed."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/structure/package.md
msgid ""
"Commit both files so other environments install the same dependency versions."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/structure/package.md
msgid "Installed packages are stored in the application `vendor/` directory."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/structure/package.md
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"> [!WARNING]\n"
"> Never edit files in `vendor/` directly. Change application configuration, extend classes, decorate services, or\n"
"> contribute fixes to the package instead.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/structure/package.md
msgid ""
"Package classes are available through Composer autoloading after "
"installation. See [Autoloading](../concept/autoloading.md)  for details."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ##
#: ../src/guide/structure/package.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Updating packages <span id=\"updating-packages\"></span>"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/structure/package.md
msgid ""
"Update a package within the version constraint recorded in `composer.json`:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Fenced code block (sh)
#: ../src/guide/structure/package.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "composer update vendor-name/package-name\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/structure/package.md
msgid "Change the accepted version constraint with `composer require`:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Fenced code block (sh)
#: ../src/guide/structure/package.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "composer require vendor-name/package-name:^2.0\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/structure/package.md
msgid ""
"After updating a Yii-aware package, Composer rebuilds Yii's configuration "
"merge plan. If you changed configuration group mappings manually, rebuild it "
"explicitly:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ##
#: ../src/guide/structure/package.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Removing packages <span id=\"removing-packages\"></span>"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/structure/package.md
msgid "Remove a package with:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Fenced code block (sh)
#: ../src/guide/structure/package.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "composer remove vendor-name/package-name\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/structure/package.md
msgid ""
"Then remove application code and configuration that referenced classes, "
"services, routes, commands, assets, migrations, or translations from that "
"package."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ##
#: ../src/guide/structure/package.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Private packages <span id=\"private-packages\"></span>"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/structure/package.md
msgid ""
"For private code, configure Composer repositories in the application "
"`composer.json`. Common options are:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: ../src/guide/structure/package.md
msgid "`vcs` for a Git repository."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: ../src/guide/structure/package.md
msgid "`path` for a local package during development."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: ../src/guide/structure/package.md
msgid "`composer` for a private Composer repository."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/structure/package.md
msgid "For example, to work with a package located next to the application:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Fenced code block (json)
#: ../src/guide/structure/package.md
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"{\n"
"    \"repositories\": [\n"
"        {\n"
"            \"type\": \"path\",\n"
"            \"url\": \"../packages/blog\"\n"
"        }\n"
"    ]\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/structure/package.md
msgid "Then install it normally:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Fenced code block (sh)
#: ../src/guide/structure/package.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "composer require vendor/blog\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/structure/package.md
msgid ""
"Read more in the [Composer repository documentation](https://getcomposer.org/"
"doc/05-repositories.md)."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ##
#: ../src/guide/structure/package.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Package configuration <span id=\"package-configuration\"></span>"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/structure/package.md
msgid ""
"Some Yii packages provide default configuration through [yiisoft/config]"
"(https://github.com/yiisoft/config).  After installation, the package "
"configuration becomes part of the vendor layer and the application can "
"override it in the root package configuration."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/structure/package.md
msgid ""
"Prefer partial overrides in application config files over copying whole "
"package config files. For example, override only the parameter or service "
"definition you need."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/structure/package.md
msgid ""
"For more details, see [Configuration](../concept/configuration.md) and "
"[Designing packages for Yii applications](designing-packages.md)."
msgstr ""
